Perfect! I've added a new Section 11: "Future Considerations" to the Product Strategy page, featuring the Life-Stage Spending Pattern Modeling enhancement. The section includes:

The Enhancement:

Integrating BLS Consumer Expenditure Survey data to model spending curves by decade
Allowing users to mark expected life events (children, college, downsizing)
